@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wmsvto(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.12 + v1 + 0.48) / (v2 + 0.46 * v0 + 0.00)) / wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.34)))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.04) / wp.exp(v2 + 0.57)) + (wp.abs(v1 + 0.16) + (v1 + 0.77 / tmp + 0.81)))
    v2 = (((v0 + 0.60 - tmp + 0.89) + wp.sin(v0 + 0.02)) + wp.cos((v2 + 0.06 * tmp + 0.15)))
    v1 = wp.sin(v1)
    data[tid] = v0
